<?xml version="1.0"?>
<Fleet xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">
  <Name>White Wing</Name>
  <Version>3</Version>
  <TotalPoints>3000</TotalPoints>
  <FactionKey>KUIPER/kuiper</FactionKey>
  <Description>Difficulty: &lt;color=yellow&gt;MODERATE&lt;/color&gt;

White Wing "Anvil De-Facto" is a wing built around Durable Firepower, Contesting Objectives, and Slugging Frontline Assets.
Built around the heavily-armed Kasr Cruiser as a survivable baseline supported by five Kyves independently serving as gunships, The goal of this fleet is to take key objectives and ground while going toe to toe with enemy heavy assets. While the Kyves can be used in a wolf pack or to support the Kasr they are at their best while contesting enemy light ships for capture points. Dread Harbinger also mounts several CBU-40U Guardians, a variant of Cubesat, able to provide soft kill or extra point defense in a pinch to their mothership. 
  </Description>
  <SortOverrideOrder>4</SortOverrideOrder>
  <ModDependencies>
    <unsignedLong>3649434947</unsignedLong>
  </ModDependencies>
